| Set a system variable to the application directory
Set ARMEdit$Dir <Obey$Dir>

| Load the application sprites
If "<Boot$OSVersion>" < "400" Then IconSprites <ARMEdit$Dir>.!Sprites Else IconSprites <ARMEdit$Dir>.4Sprites
